{"tid":940723,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗訓練課程","createTime":"2018-12-14T07:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T09:22:16.000Z","uid":178635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52870edfb0c5633177296d97a5e9374b0b2069e6","tid":940723,"uid":178635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"屋企第一次養狗狗，宜家狗狗都有10個月大啦<br />\n但仲係成日咬人，中意搶紙巾咬，咬門框，唔定點去廁所，仲要唔比人洗耳仔抹眼，一掂就咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我同屋企人勁頭痛唔知點教好<br />\n想話教佢咩叫no咩叫sit佢都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗諗下不如帶佢去狗狗訓練課程<br />\n希望1歲前叫做無咁曳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家既狗狗有無都上過訓練課程？有無好推介呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見到愛協有，有啲私人既狗狗學校都有，但就唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲係學生未有咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有無好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e07398c9607e61ce2f4fdd5608263e119a6c280","tid":940723,"uid":198165,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"叫佢比手/坐，唔聽話，琴佢一巴<br />\n試多幾次 done ✅ <br />\n邊度唔比屙尿屙屎，指住果度，琴佢一巴<br />\n試多幾次 done ✅"},{"pid":"c13543a503fdea99f834302353f363910dfdc6c8","tid":940723,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"上網好多有教學 睇下你有咩最想改善，有心一定教到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa646503d90d62e4e0506f310e1c5b84319149d","tid":940723,"uid":178635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e07398c9607e61ce2f4fdd5608263e119a6c280","tid":940723,"uid":198165,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"叫佢比手/坐，唔聽話，琴佢一巴<br />\n試多幾次 done ✅ <br />\n邊度唔比屙尿屙屎，指住果度，琴佢一巴<br />\n試多幾次 done ✅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:59:25.000Z","msg":"我屋企人好似都有試過，會